#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/transform_distort_perspective/mirror.rst:15
msgid "Mirror"
msgstr "Spiegelen"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/transform_distort_perspective/mirror.rst:17
msgid ""
"This effect/filter mirrors your image in any direction. It can also flip"
" it "
"horizontally and vertically.  Compare :ref:`effects-flip_vertically`,"
" :ref:"
"`effects-flip_horizontally` and :ref:`effects-flippo` effects."
msgstr ""
"Dit effect/filter spiegelt uw afbeelding in elke richting. Het kan het "
"ook horizontaal en verticaal spiegelen.  Vergelijk :ref:"
"`effects-flip_vertically`, :ref:`effects-flip_horizontally` en :ref:"
"`effects-flippo` effects."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/transform_distort_perspective/mirror.rst:19
msgid "The effect does not have keyframes."
msgstr "Dit effect heeft geen keyframes."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/transform_distort_perspective/mirror.rst:27
msgid "Mirror effect"
msgstr "Effect spiegelen"

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/transform_distort_perspective/mirror.rst:29
msgid ""
"**Mirroring direction** - Set the mirroring axis. Options are"
" **Horizontal** "
"(default), **Vertical**, **Diagonal**, and **X Diagonal**. By default,"
" the "
"right and bottom half are mirrored. Use :guilabel:`Invert` to change this."
msgstr ""
"**Richting van spiegeling** - stelt de as van spiegeling in. Opties zijn "
"**Horizontaal** (standaard), **Verticaal**, **Diagonaal**, en "
"**X-diagonaal**. Standaard worden de rechter- en onderhelft gespiegeld. "
"Gebruik :guilabel:`Inverteren` om dit te wijzigen."

#: ../../effects_and_compositions/video_effects/transform_distort_perspective/mirror.rst:31
msgid ""
"**Invert** - Invert the direction (not effective on **Flip** and **Flop**)"
msgstr ""
"**Inverteren** - inverteert de richting (niet effectief bij **Flip** en "
"**Flop**)"

